.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-REPUTATION" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-reputation \- show connection and channel info for a peer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-reputation
.I peer_id
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns connectivity status and aggregate channel capacity for the specified peer.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"peer_id":..., "connected":bool, "num_channels":N, "total_capacity_msat":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-peer-score (1),
.BR lightning-peer-alias (1)
